        <updateDate>2023-04-14T14:11:47Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Shell Company Abuse Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes it unlawful to establish or use a corporation, company, or other entity with the intent to conceal an election contribution or donation by a foreign national.</p> <p>A violator is subject to criminal penalties&#8212;a fine, a prison term of up to five years, or both.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
